<section>
  <div class="maxwidth section space-y-6 leading-relaxed text-gray-800">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-700">Indivirtus Healthcare Services Pvt. Ltd.</h3>

    <p>
      <strong>Indivirtus Healthcare Services Pvt. Ltd.</strong> is a leading
      <strong>Contract Research Organization (CRO)</strong>, dedicated to supporting the global
      <strong>pharmaceutical</strong>, <strong>biotech</strong>, and <strong>healthcare</strong> industries with specialized
      regulatory, scientific, and compliance solutions.
    </p>

    <p>
      We are recognized as market leaders in the <strong>toxicological risk assessment of impurities</strong> and the preparation
      of <strong>ADE/PDE/OEL/OEB reports</strong>, helping organizations worldwide ensure
      <strong>patient safety</strong> and achieve <strong>regulatory compliance</strong>.
    </p>

    <p>Our core service offerings include:</p>

    <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong>Toxicological Risk Assessment</strong> — Impurities, ADE/PDE/OEL/OEB reports for regulatory compliance.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Regulatory Affairs</strong> — Dossier preparation, regulatory strategy, and global submissions.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Calibration Services</strong> — Comprehensive calibration solutions through our
        <strong>NABL-accredited laboratory</strong>.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Pharmacovigilance</strong> — End-to-end safety monitoring and reporting.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Greenfield & Brownfield Turnkey Project Consulting</strong> — Facility design, compliance readiness, and
        project management.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      At Indivirtus, we blend <strong>scientific expertise</strong> with deep <strong>regulatory insight</strong> to deliver
      <strong>precise, reliable, and actionable solutions</strong> — enabling our clients to bring safe, high-quality products
      to market with confidence and efficiency.
    </p>

    <p>
      Guided by a culture of <strong>quality</strong>, <strong>integrity</strong>, and <strong>client-centricity</strong
      >, Indivirtus Healthcare Services is a trusted partner to
      <strong
        >leading pharmaceutical companies, contract manufacturers, healthcare organizations, and regulatory agencies
        worldwide</strong
      >.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-700">Your Compliance. Our Commitment.</h3>

    <p>
      Partner with Indivirtus to simplify regulatory complexity, accelerate timelines, and uphold the highest standards
      of <strong>patient</strong> and <strong>product safety</strong>.
    </p>
  </div>
